MATRIARCHAL CLANS AS IN WOMEN IN POSITIONS OF POWER, YESSSSS

This book has everything a fantasy lover could ever wish for:
- Unique world rich with diverse nations, religions, politics, places, history, gods, and, of course, magic;
- A cast of distinct and complex characters coming from different backgrounds;
- An interesting premise which keeps you intrigued from the very beginning;
- Beautiful writing which breathes life into the world and makes you care about the characters.

